P.title: Will Jimmy Neutron be US president in 2025?
P.body: Resolves YES if Jimmy Neutron is president by the end of 2025. Resolves NO otherwise.

para_P.title: Is it likely that Jimmy Neutron will become the President of the United States by the end of 2025?
para_P.body: Resolves YES if Jimmy Neutron assumes the presidency by the conclusion of 2025. Resolves NO otherwise.
